 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=yiliamar>Yiliamar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/01 4:08:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Im a noob to the Wizzy classs</span><hr size=1> Research is a pain in the arse.  It blows big, gooy chunks.  I hate it.<br>
