</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uiudar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iudar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/1/01 8:26:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Im a noob to the Wizzy classs</span><hr size=1> Wizards are awesome.<br>
<br>
I love my Wizard, he was the first (accually third, never make a human ranger in Surefall, you'll never find your way our.  Never make a Wizard and dump everything into Wisdom) character I ever made, and he is still my highest.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Try to avoid a lot of the negativism that you hear on the boards.  There are a lot of whiners (myself included sometimes =P), but even then there is great knowledge to be gained.<br>
<br>
<br>
The lessons I learned here helped me get through my 20s when I was just a lurker.<br>
<br>
Thaught me the basics of Quad-Kiting, which friends helped me master.<br>
<br>
They are always willing to give suggestions for new hunting grounds, most of them very good suggestions.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
--<br>
<br>
Reseach:  Isn't bad early on.  level 16 - 24 I had very little difficulty with, both getting the Runes and doing the Combines.<br>
<br>
After 29, it gets more difficult and frustrating though.  It is worth the effort, as some of our best spells either research/dragon drops (Ice Comet), or research only, like Circle of Force.<br>
<br>
-<br>
<br>
Soloing:  Until you get snare at 29, you're pretty much restricted to Root and Nuke, and bumming a SoW and learning to kite.<br>
<br>
Enter your Mid-Teens, take your pillar spells to North Karana and learn to Quad the bettles there.  I wish I had known that when I was at the level, I'd have advanced so much faster.<br>
<br>
<br>
-<br>
Finally....<br>
<br>
Be weary of Al'Kabor, he talks a good game, and presents himself as a Master, but he is a sham.  His spells are good for raising your research skills, but little else. <p><TABLE ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=460 COLS=1 BORDER=1 BGCOLOR=#FF0000>
